headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on The Diamond Casino Podium
content:
Make sure to visit the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort this week and give the Lucky Wheel a spin for the opportunity to win the Ocelot Ardent — a two-door with twin machine guns built into the front bumper — whirling atop the podium nearby.

If you win the top prize, your Podium Vehicle will be delivered to your selected Garage.
